Version 2.0.0
    - Do not use wlr-layer-shell protocol.
    - Use wlr-foreign-toplevel-management for show views on multiple displays as fullscreen
    - Support for Themes - Four default themes available: Default, Sidebar, Compact, Aerial (incomplete)
    - Support for sway, wayfire, and an inbuilt compositor, greetwl
    - Support for suspend, hibernate, shutdown and reboot

Version 1.0
    - Inital Release
    - Some working parts
    - Few bugs
